{
  "texts": [
    "Bench-Capon and Dunne (2007) present four properties that mathematical reasoning is said to have, but which argumentation is said to lack.",
    "We do not think that any of these properties hold of mathematical reasoning but not of argumentation; however, unsurprisingly, full analysis is beyond the present scope.",
    "We thus comment on only their fourth property, which relates directly to the issue we have already raised.",
    "This fourth property is expressed verbatim by these two authors as follows:",
    "[I]n mathematical reasoning."
  ]
}